## Infrastructure Decision

The full research is at `context/foundation/infrastructure.md`. Reference it with `@context/foundation/infrastructure.md` when you need the complete document.

### Key Facts

- Platform: Vercel (Hobby tier, $0)
- Runner-up: Railway
- Region: Frankfurt (fra1) or Paris (cdg1), ~20-30ms to Poland
- DB: Neon Postgres via Vercel Marketplace (auto DATABASE_URL injection)
- Rollback: `vercel rollback <url>` (instant, but DB migrations don't auto-rollback)
- Function timeout: 10s on Hobby (monitor tRPC procedure execution time)

### When to Load Full Doc

- First deploy or changing deploy config — Getting Started steps
- Debugging production issues — operational story (logs, rollback, secrets)
- Evaluating platform limits — risk register with mitigations
- Considering platform migration — full comparison matrix with scoring
